Well, color me curious, what did you do? And who did you take?

671
01:02:12,427 --> 01:02:15,271
弄痛你了 就跟我说 Milton
Let me know if I hurt you, Milton.

672
01:02:15,363 --> 01:02:17,240
我刚才想把她抢回来的
I tried to get her back.

673
01:02:18,099 --> 01:02:19,737
真的
I really did.

674
01:02:19,835 --> 01:02:21,143
我知道
I know.

675
01:02:21,703 --> 01:02:25,310
去他妈的恶魔崇拜者 他们真他妈让我抓狂
Fucking devil worshippers. They freak me the fuck out.

676
01:02:25,874 --> 01:02:29,117
他们不该动用那些力量的 现在却随便动用 快气死我了
Messing with powers they ought not to. Turns my shit white.

677
01:02:29,177 --> 01:02:31,054
这些都是虚幻的
None of it's real.

678
01:02:32,314 --> 01:02:36,854
Milton 不是的 UFO 大脚野人 还有鬼都是扯淡的
No, Milton. UFOs and bigfoot and ghosts, that's bullshit.

679
01:02:37,686 --> 01:02:39,597
恶魔是真的
Devils and demons.

680
01:02:41,289 --> 01:02:44,133
一旦你开启了那些门 就由不得你关上了
Once you open those doors, you just can't close them.

681
01:02:44,559 --> 01:02:46,334
