- 用来施绞刑的树  - 猜对了
- Hanging tree.  - Yeah.

745
01:09:19,854 --> 01:09:23,996
上一次绞刑是在38年 他们留下了那棵树用来奚落囚犯
Last hanging was in '38. They left the tree to taunt the inmates.

746
01:09:24,492 --> 01:09:26,403
谷歌地图说 开车要8小时
Google Maps says it's an eight-hour drive.

747
01:09:26,461 --> 01:09:27,997
- 我们会在...  - Webster
- We should be...  - Webster,

748
01:09:29,430 --> 01:09:31,432
- 我要你留下来  - 什么?
- I need you to stay here.  - What?

749
01:09:31,866 --> 01:09:34,403
不行 你上次就是一个人去的
No. You went alone last time.

750
01:09:34,535 --> 01:09:35,878
这次不是
I'm not going alone.

751
01:09:36,371 --> 01:09:39,215
你是要带那个小萝莉 不带我吗?
Are you gonna take that little girl over me?

752
01:09:40,208 --> 01:09:42,279
把弹壳都给我吧
Give me the shells.

753
01:09:43,511 --> 01:09:47,049
你真是个该死的矛盾体 你知道吗?
You're a goddamned walking contradiction, you know that?

754
01:09:47,215 --> 01:09:49,217
你有多少次想要伸张正义
How many times you walk towards the straight and narrow

755
01:09:49,317 --> 01:09:51,991
最后却以牺牲别人而收场?
only to get covered up in someone else's blood?

756
01:09:53,054 --> 01:09:55,000
你这次又要以谁生命终结来收场?
Whose blood are you gonna end up covered in this time?

757
01:09:55,223 --> 01:09:58,363
- 这次不一样  - 是吗?
- This time it's different.  - Is it?

758
01:10:18,346 --> 01:10:20,292
他不一起来吗?
He's not coming?

759
01:10:20,715 --> 01:10:21,955
Piper啊
Piper,

760
01:10:22,583 --> 01:10:25,063
我需要你 但我不会对你说谎
I need you. But I won't lie to you.

761
01:10:26,120 --> 01:10:27,929
这事很难办
This is going to be rough.

762
01:10:28,623 --> 01:10:30,102
你确定要跟我一起吗?
Are you sure about this?

763
01:10:30,291 --> 01:10:33,204
一直以来 我的生活除了等待一无所有
My whole life has been nothing but waiting.

764
01:10:33,761 --> 01:10:37,732
等人点餐 等一个混蛋 我一直等着生活有意义的那一天
Waiting on tables, waiting on fools, waiting for it just to mean something.

765
01:10:38,499 --> 01:10:39,773
现在 终于让我等到了
And now, it means something.

766
01:10:40,268 --> 01:10:41,872
我跟定你了
I'm with you until the end.

767
01:11:09,263 --> 01:11:11,140
我们现在干吗?
What do we do?

768
01:11:11,232 --> 01:11:12,836
没事
Nothing yet.

769
01:11:13,134 --> 01:11:14,477
该死
Shit.

770
01:11:27,448 --> 01:11:30,395
你们只要把他们逼向这边 剩下的交给我们
You just keep driving them to us. We'll do the rest.

771
01:11:30,451 --> 01:11:33,523
记得在爆炸之前脱身
And make sure you peel off before the fireworks.

772
01:11:36,657 --> 01:11:38,898
警官们 集合!
Troopers, fall in!

773
01:11:42,530 --> 01:11:45,909
