Gentlemen, these two have killed two of our own.

774
01:11:46,000 --> 01:11:48,810
我知道你们很想让他们偿命
I know you want to make them pay.

775
01:11:48,870 --> 01:11:52,477
所以 当我下令瞄准轮胎时
Therefore, when I tell you to aim for their tires,

776
01:11:52,540 --> 01:11:54,349
就是在说
what I mean is

777
01:11:54,442 --> 01:11:58,515
