很好
Very well then.

780
01:12:03,618 --> 01:12:05,325
现在
Please,

781
01:12:06,421 --> 01:12:08,662
瞄准轮胎
aim for their tires.

782
01:12:18,266 --> 01:12:20,940
前面会有更多
There'll be even more ahead.

783
01:12:21,202 --> 01:12:23,204
继续开吧
Just keep driving.

784
01:12:25,540 --> 01:12:27,349
抱歉
I'm sorry.

785
01:12:41,022 --> 01:12:42,262
来了
Here we go.

786
01:12:44,992 --> 01:12:46,369
穷途末路了 伙计
End of the line, folks.

787
01:12:46,494 --> 01:12:48,804
举起双手 慢慢走出车子
Step out of the vehicle with your hands raised.

788
